  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Kineflex Spinal System is no worse than the Charite Spinal System in patients with single
      level degenerative disc disease at L4/5 or L5/S1.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The Kineflex disc is a 3-piece modular design consisting of 2 cobalt chrome molybdenum (CCM)
      end-plates and a fully articulating CCM core. The system is available in 3 foot print sizes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
